Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.56,0:00:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.58,0:00:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空好藍 你露出了微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.25,0:00:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的一句話使內心相繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.39,0:00:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上鞋子敞開門扉的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.10,0:00:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你重合的景色使我心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.98,0:00:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢\N加速的心跳無法壓抑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.98,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人共同感受  季節不斷更替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.46,0:01:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可取代的瞬間\N編織著邂逅的物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.43,0:01:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對紛飛的櫻花許下心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.44,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.41,0:01:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花盛開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.92,0:01:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四話 櫻花樹下的金絲雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.72,0:01:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢那傢伙又亂買東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.96,0:01:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.04,0:01:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.77,0:01:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.94,0:01:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.11,0:01:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麵包！ （跟內褲音近）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.48,0:02:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥好色喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.75,0:02:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，絕對不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在說內褲\N是麵包，我的炒麵麵包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.46,0:02:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是吃剩放在冰箱裡的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的用詞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.56,0:02:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是吃剩的\N是我存起來當早餐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.40,0:02:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別吃掉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.54,0:02:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.77,0:02:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放了一個晚上的炒麵麵包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.71,0:02:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入味的醬料會跟麵包調和\N蘊育出絕佳的共鳴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.64,0:02:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.51,0:02:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你起來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.02,0:02:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.18,0:02:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻，妳快點撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.25,0:02:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.49,0:02:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點出去\N我可不想一大早就惹麻煩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又何必如此呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.59,0:02:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別用時代劇的語氣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.53,0:02:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點出去，妳這隻撒野的小貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.04,0:02:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不起床上學就會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.78,0:03:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.55,0:03:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.45,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要臉～哥哥大笨蛋～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.32,0:03:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳誤會了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才剛睡醒就讓我全力衝刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢那傢伙真的想要我的命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才早上七點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，那就去學校擦黑板吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是幫大家擦書桌也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.31,0:03:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的炒麵麵包…我的紅薑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.83,0:05:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是琴梨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好悅耳的歌聲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.85,0:05:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎不是個壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是寶貴的畫面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼誇張嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼誇張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清純可愛的學園偶像白河琴梨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.24,0:06:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅漂亮還處處為人著想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說宛如能看透別人的內心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能看透內心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就是這麼的了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位白河小姐唱歌時的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是Z級的寶貴畫面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能看透人心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.21,0:06:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吃期待已久的炒麵麵包吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福利社的阿姨又拿錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（本日已售完）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買到最後一個海鮮炒麵麵包囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是幸運呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烤麵包的話還有一個喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.79,0:07:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.46,0:07:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炒麵麵包…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.03,0:07:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這股香味是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到炒麵火鍋居然這麼好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炒麵火鍋？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.91,0:07:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大概被炒麵麵包討厭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.49,0:07:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意的話就交換吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交換？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我的不幸交換妳的幸福嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是白河啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要跟我交換麵包嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不正是和我生離死別的\N炒麵麵包兄弟嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是滿足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是個巧合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到所有的麵包\N都回到各自的歸宿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.72,0:08:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳怎麼知道\N炒麵麵包是我的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.86,0:08:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是巧合，不自覺就這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.09,0:08:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不自覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，不自覺就這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.30,0:08:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不自覺就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過無所謂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已經吃到炒麵麵包了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.67,0:08:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.84,0:08:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳聞中能看透人心的\N白河琴梨善解人意的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是受歡迎的祕密呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說太誇張了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到這個傳聞是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是這麼說我的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我說得好像有超能力一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是最頂級的讚美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試著謙虛接受不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.06,0:08:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學覺得\N可以看透人心是件好事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話會很方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.34,0:09:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比方說在玩對戰遊戲時\N可以知道對方要出什麼招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.11,0:09:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩牌時也能知道對方有什麼牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考試時也可以考滿分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像浪費在很沒用的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.22,0:09:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別人的內心還是別看透比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.28,0:09:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總不能說我看得到朝倉的心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.89,0:09:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看到別人的內心\N就可以知道對方在想什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白河琴梨好可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是校園裡的偶像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天爺把一切都給了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望她早點走出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.74,0:10:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她穿泳裝一定很迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於下課了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家打個電動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家看太宰的著作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.29,0:10:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，今天輪到你們打掃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也夠了快動手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.17,0:10:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有人在吹魔笛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.44,0:10:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是箂茵河的女神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.95,0:11:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道琴梨要唱歌就變這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.69,0:11:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人真是現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.16,0:11:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是，早知道應該收門票的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會給聲樂社造成困擾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.16,0:11:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的\N是他們拜託妳幫忙代唱的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我們是被拜託來幫忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.10,0:11:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-琴梨\N-加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像動物園裡的熊貓一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是古老的譬喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不唱嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨她好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.50,0:11:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有男朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圍巾蜥蜴？美西螈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.14,0:11:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是很老土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨真的好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（不要用…）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.85,0:12:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真是善解人意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（這種方式…）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可是高嶺之花呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（看著我…求求你們…）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-栗鼠？海獅？\N-琴梨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.41,0:13:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.95,0:13:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼朝倉同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.99,0:13:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉琴梨拜託你照顧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得趕去開教職員會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真不懂得為別人著想呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會影響到你的推甄成績喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.93,0:13:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的可愛妹妹如果有個萬一\N我可是絕對不原諒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.88,0:13:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親姊妹的個性竟然差這麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.97,0:13:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是朝倉同學在陪我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.64,0:14:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好像鱉一樣不放開我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.78,0:14:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.15,0:14:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…送到這裡就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.99,0:14:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，那麼再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.49,0:14:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是送妳回家好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.16,0:14:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有個萬一的話\N我會被曆老師殺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她會怎麼罵我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.17,0:14:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，不過我真的沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓你擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的，別放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就當作是中午的炒麵麵包\N以及早上的謝禮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.88,0:14:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在一棵大櫻花樹下唱歌對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我不是故意要偷看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.59,0:14:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是看妳唱得那麼好\N我也不方便打擾妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.83,0:15:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時雖然感覺有人在看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻不會覺得討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.71,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛也是感覺好溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.04,0:15:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學的內心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢那傢伙也應該氣消了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說那是不可抗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.09,0:15:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，並不是我不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.23,0:15:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.57,0:15:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.57,0:15:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.10,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是福利社賣的炒麵麵包？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正確答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.24,0:15:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，難道妳出陣前往\N化為男人戰場的福利社？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.45,0:15:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為早上我好像說得太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.26,0:16:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想說這樣哥哥應該會很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.26,0:16:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.02,0:16:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，今天的戀愛學園如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.92,0:16:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴梨的歌聲百聽不厭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.49,0:16:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到朝倉是炒麵麵包迷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.93,0:16:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炒麵火鍋只要加入高湯\N麵就會很容易糊掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請大家盡快吃掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以高湯也是炒麵醬的味道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.67,0:16:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一話居然是貓耳女僕\N要和大家住在同一個屋簷下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.50,0:16:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，音夢和哥哥的飲食\N看得到一絲曙光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.21,0:16:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你流鼻血了啦\N（第五話  因為是女僕…）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣的故事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.96,0:17:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒐集心的碎片  想趕快送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.17,0:17:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎快要滿溢  真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.37,0:17:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人漫步於鈴音輕響的樹蔭下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.98,0:17:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合而為一的影子\N高興地凝視著夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.39,0:17:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花之雨紛飛著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.99,0:17:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由樹梢陽光所籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.73,0:17:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在累積於胸口的哀傷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.21,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更替的季節與不變的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.35,0:18:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會演奏通往未來的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.56,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛總是能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.56,0:18:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.16,0:18:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（緊依不離☆）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.98,0:19:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捲曲身子的話 根本無法呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.62,0:19:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓精神振作一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.36,0:19:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯你也辦得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.90,0:19:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到你沒有精神的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.90,0:19:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是無法放著你不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.61,0:19:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話通通告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.18,0:19:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕  沒時間談戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.25,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了  每次都碰到頭痛問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒辦法囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.90,0:20:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿心期待的胸口悸動\NHI! FLY! HlGH!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.94,0:20:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將來要突然跟你緊依不離☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.47,0:20:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要耍點任性\NHI! FLY! HIGH!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.88,0:20:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還在準備戀愛中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.46,0:20:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,窗外看得見紅色的晚霞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.87,0:20:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耀眼的太陽也像這樣西沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.34,0:20:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放學的廣播  必須回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.11,0:20:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腳步聲響遍安靜的走廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.02,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回神時我正在奔跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.66,0:21:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕  要說什麼才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.76,0:21:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了  想讓你溫柔守護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時會這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.17,0:21:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鹿亂撞的胸口悸動\NHI! FLY! HIGH!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.41,0:21:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將來要突然跟你緊依不離☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.42,0:21:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想聽你說喜歡我\NHI! FLY! HIGH!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.36,0:21:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還要一陣子 少女修行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.39,0:22:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿心期待的胸口悸動\NHI! FLY! HIGH!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.40,0:22:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將來要突然跟你緊依不離☆
